課題<br />\n你其中一個課題係<br />\n獨立於自己<br />\n不再受他人影響你身心<br />\n帶苦比你<br />\n<br />\n你屋企人好似落重注咁<br />\n啫係你屋企背景好好<br />\n而你應該主攻神科<br />\n一條咁好既路<br />\n你應該好有大志<br />\n對未來充滿希望同信心<br />\n<br />\n但你正正相反<br />\n你對自己無自信<br />\n對世界好無安全感<br />\n枉你讀咁多佛理<br />\n但你一D野都學唔到<br />\n<br />\n你不能放下我執<br />\n不能不被身口耳業影響<br />\n不能禪定<br />\n<br />\n一D抵禦力都無<br />\n任由外界業力通過你身心<br />\n你只係o係度背書<br />\n你無實行過<br />\n領悟當中既深層含義<br />\n你讀唔通<br />\n<br />\n有咩辦法可以解決呢？<br />\n你咁鐘意睇佛學<br />\n<a href=\"http://di-shui-chan-house.blogspot.com/2013/09/blog-post_9331.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdi-shui-chan-house.blogspot.com%2F2013%2F09%2Fblog-post_9331.html%3Fm%3D1&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BROHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=35a8807f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://di-shui-chan-house.blogspot.com/2013/09/blog-post_9331.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n入面現代用語加上顯淺事例詳細解脫<br />\n如何放下我執<br />\n<br />\n禪定入門<br />\n<a href=\"https://zenbuddhist.pixnet.net/blog/post/2122022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzenbuddhist.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F2122022&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BROHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=ad80426f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zenbuddhist.pixnet.net/blog/post/2122022</a>"},{"pid":"5e20a04526e276288181f2ca1a323b0673bc4c40","tid":1875439,"uid":85805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef9453e66f7e32c108af743e0eb996030085194c","tid":1875439,"uid":125898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c916b8ef4ad9b4ea041993653568e41e3c0d5e8","tid":1875439,"uid":85805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66b107919bd7d81f616160b0f01efc1240974da8","tid":1875439,"uid":125898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"你個人咁得意既<br />\n你講野無重點既？<br />\n<br />\n你等於作文無主旨一樣<br />\n讀者係睇唔明你寫梗咩？<br />\n比你遇到大師<br />\n都一堆問號<br />\n然就直接走啦<br />\n<br />\n你而家最最最煩既係咩？<br />\n只有一個ga 咋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:46:48.000Z","msg":"人生每一步每一句都係重點<br />\n我講嘢係幾玄<img src=\"/assets/